   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>This definitely makes sense. Putting in 0.11.01 for now; we can easily push it
out to 0.11.02 but I feel this should be done sooner rather than later. This
would be an ideal bug for someone new to learn about Django views and templates,
and migrations.

As for layout, I'm thinking something like "Homepage: &lt;URL HERE&gt;" in the "About
&lt;PROJECT NAME&gt;" box in the top right, either above or below the programming
language note (and an edit box either above or below the programming language
edit box). Thoughts?</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
