    <pre>The project editing screen, e.g. <a href="http://openhatch.org/+projedit/Keryx">http://openhatch.org/+projedit/Keryx</a> , could 
have a part of it that shows (and lets the user edit) the project's homepage URL. 
Then we could display that somewhere.

Marking as bitesize -- this should be fairly easy.</pre>
   </td>
